Taiwanese scientific weather column format with vivid imagery about typhoon track patterns, implying an educational or cultural article title suggesting local impacts.

The phrase "每當西太平洋副高東進時，受其影響的台灣" strongly implies continuation referencing Taiwan's vulnerability or weather experiences — likely a phrase about "常來的強颱" or similar seasonal context.

Final token "台灣" is mid-noun phrase ("台灣"), part of an introductory clause structure ("每当強颱來臨時...台灣"), strongly expecting a noun like "地區便處於警戒" or "的百姓常感不安" or "往往遭遇颱風與梅雨的雙重";
